Invocation Name: prairie sounds
des:
Let the sounds of the prairie lull you right to sleep. 

All you need to do is say Alexa start Prairie Sounds, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to leave on while you are asleep, to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
